-- Maersk Says CEO Smedegaard Andersen to Return to Company Today
-- B y   F r a n c e s   S c h w a r t z k o p f f
-- 2012-05-07T07:10:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-07/maersk-says-ceo-smedegaard-andersen-to-return-to-company-today.html
A.P.Moeller-Maersk A/S said Chief
Executive Officer Nils Smedegaard Andersen will return to the
company as of today after undergoing heart surgery.  “The company continues to be full of strength while I was
absent,” Smedegaard Andersen said in the statement. “There’s a
lot of activity in our markets and lots of inititives and
challenges that I look forward to handling together with the
rest of the management team and our employees.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Frances Schwartzkopff in Copenhagen at 
 fschwartzko1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
